OL,3,CWoman to face court charged with death
OL,4,Cby dangerous driving after school crash
OL,6,FThe driver of a 44 that crashed into
OL,7,Fa south-east London primary school
OL,8,Fwill appear in court charged with
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving
OL,10,Fafter two eight-year-old girls were
OL,11,Fkilled.
OL,13,FClaire Freemantle, 49, is accused of
OL,14,Ftwo counts of causing death by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving and seven counts of
OL,16,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving following the incident at The
OL,18,FStudy Prep school in Wimbledon in July
OL,19,F2023.
OL,26,@nD@ROZ
