OL,3,CWoman to face court charged with death
OL,4,Cby dangerous driving after school crash
OL,6,FSchoolgirls Nuria Sajjad and Selena
OL,7,FLau died in the crash as the school
OL,8,Fwas celebrating the last day of the
OL,9,Fsummer term.
OL,11,FFreemantle will appear at Westminster
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,14,FHer lawyers previously said she would
OL,15,Fplead not guilty to the charges.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
