OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781610480
OL,3,CWoman to face court charged with death
OL,4,Cby dangerous driving after school crash
OL,6,FThe charges came in May after the
OL,7,Fgirls' families criticised the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police for its
OL,9,Finvestigation into the crash, with the
OL,10,Fforce saying in June 2024 that the
OL,11,Fdriver had suffered an epileptic
OL,12,Fseizure and would face no criminal
OL,13,Fcharges.
OL,15,FFreemantle, of Edge Hill, Wimbledon,
OL,16,Fwas rearrested and released under
OL,17,Finvestigation in January last year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
